snippet.title: Battle Baseball (Famicom) - Gameplay
snippet.description: Battle Baseball is a 1993 NES / Famicom baseball video game starring characters from Godzilla, Kamen Rider, Ultraman, and Gundam. This is a 9-inning game of the Godzilla team versus the Gundam team.
